OL,3,CSix children saved by coastguard team
OL,4,Cin 'major incident'
OL,6,FSix young children have been rescued
OL,7,Fby Port Talbot Coastguard Team after
OL,8,Fthey got into 'serious difficulty' in
OL,9,Fthe sea.
OL,11,FThe 'major incident' happened Sunday,
OL,12,F24 August at around 8.30pm in the sea
OL,13,Foff the slipway at Aberavon Beach,
OL,14,FPort Talbot.
OL,16,FThe Coastguard Team were made aware of
OL,17,Fthe report from a member of the public.
