OL,3,CSix children saved by coastguard team
OL,4,Cin 'major incident'
OL,6,FCoastguard Rescue Officers (CROs) were
OL,7,Fimmediately on scene, deploying a
OL,8,Fthrow line to bring three children
OL,9,Fsafely ashore.
OL,11,FThey then entered the water to bring
OL,12,Fthe remaining casualties to safety.
OL,14,FAll six children were taken to the
OL,15,FCoastguard station, where emergency
OL,16,Fcasualty care was carried out. They
OL,17,Fwere then transferred to ambulance
OL,18,Fservices for further medical
OL,19,Fevaluation.
